N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 §§ 8186-25.1 - Definitions

State Regulations

Definitions of terms used in this Subpart are set forth in
former 9 NYCRR section 186-1.1, as repealed in 1998 and set forth in section
8185-1.1
of this Title and sections
1801
and
1901
of the Real Property Tax Law, and the

Subpart of rules which refers to the base survey immediately preceding the
update survey. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20
§§
8186-25.1

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
